Layer ham, mizuna, and onion over 2 slices of bread. Place mozzarella cheese on top. Spread sliced sausage evenly over cheese. Cover with the other 2 slices of bread. Preheat a sandwich maker according to manufacturer's instructions. Brush plates with melted butter. Cook sandwiches in the preheated sandwich maker until crispy, about 5 minutes. Cut each sandwich in half before serving.